<BaseLayout title="About — s_0 studio">
<section>
  <h1>About</h1>
  <p>
    S_0 refers to a point of origin—where each project is defined before it is developed.
    Each project is developed through a structured process. Spatial layout defines the project. 
    Materials are selected with restraint. Details are resolved before execution. The objective is not variation, but clarity—achieved through control, consistency, and precision.
  </p>
</section>



  <!-- Founder -->
  <div class="team-founder">
    <figure>
      <img src="/images/Andi Dumitru2.jpg" alt="Founder portrait" />
      <figcaption>
        <strong>dott. arch. Andi Dumitru</strong><br />
        Founder / Architect
      </figcaption>
    </figure>

    <p class="founder-bio">
      Fully licensed architect, with studies in the UK and Milan at leading universities, and
      extensive professional experience across Romania, the United Kingdom,
      and Italy. Has worked with award-winning practices on projects spanning
      multiple scales and typologies.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p>
   The studio works with a limited number of projects at a time. Each project is developed with direct involvement, controlled timelines, and clear documentation. 
   To be able to deliver the projects execution at their peak we collaborate with a number of constructors manufacturers and  suppliers that ensure quality and on-time delivery. 
  </p>
</section>
  <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">
    Request a consultation
  </a>
</section>

</section>
</BaseLayout>
